<sect1 id="dir_ee142403c4fa16dd4361af2a521a19d8_1autotoc_md442">
<title>helios::engine::modules::rendering::viewport</title><para>State-based viewport management for conditional rendering.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_ee142403c4fa16dd4361af2a521a19d8_1autotoc_md443">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides a policy-driven system for determining which viewports should be rendered based on the current game and match state. This enables different viewports to be shown during different game phases (e.g., menu viewport during pause, game viewport during play).</para>
</sect1>
